channel.title: Looking for a developer on my upcoming server 718/723
channel.description: I am working on developing a server using the Matrix 718/723 base. Seeing as I don't have all the time in the world during the summer I need a coder to develope with me so that we can accomplish many things in a shorter amount of time. You must have a knowledge of 667+ coding. I need someone who is willing to devote alot of time into making a very advanced server with me. Skype: mabrox97 Add me if interested. For the server I also own a domain and a vps.
